languages.text: "Ты победил{mf||а} Сумерки, ты сразил{mf||а} Зарю. Но только одну из нас. Только одну!"
"You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"
languages.original_text: "Ты победил{mf||а} Сумерки, ты сразил{mf||а} Зарю. Но только одну из нас. Только одну!"

traits.locale_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You struck down Aurora. But she was just one of us. Just one!"
"You vanquished Twilight. You struck down Aurora. But she was just one of us. Just one!"
"You vanquished Twilight. You snuffed Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"
"You vanquished Twilight. You snuffed Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

languages.text: "Ihr habt Zwielicht besiegt. Ihr habt Aurora niedergestreckt. Doch sie war nur eine von uns. Hört Ihr?"
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: "Ihr habt Zwielicht besiegt. Ihr habt Aurora ausgelöscht. Doch sie war nur eine von uns. Hört Ihr?"

languages.text: « Vous avez vaincu Crépuscule. Vous avez abattu Aurore. Mais elle n'était que l'une des nôtres. Vous entendez ? »
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: « Vous avez vaincu Crépuscule. Vous avez tué Aurore. Mais elle n'était que l'une des nôtres. Vous entendez ? »

languages.text: “你击败了‘暮光’，还杀死了‘极光’。然而，她仅仅是我们之中的一员，你听到了吗？”
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: “你击败了暮光。你还扼杀了极光，但她仅仅是我们之中的一员。你听到了吗？”

languages.text: 「お前は薄明を倒した。お前はオーロラを斬りつけた。しかし、アレは我々のひとりにすぎない。我が声が聞こえるか？」
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: 「お前は薄明を倒した。お前はオーロラを殺した。しかし、アレは我々のひとりにすぎない。我が声が聞こえるか？」

languages.text: «Venciste a Crepúsculo. Abatiste a Aurora. Pero era solo una de muchos. ¿Me oyes?».
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: «Venciste a Crepúsculo. Extinguiste a Aurora. Pero era solo una de muchos. ¿Me oyes?».

languages.text: "Seher'i yendin. Aurora'yı katlettin. Fakat o yalnızca birimizdi. Duydun mu beni?"
languages.original_text: "You vanquished Twilight. You cut down Aurora. But she was only one of us. You hear me?"

traits.locale_text: "Seher'i hakladınız. Aurora'yı alt ettiniz. Fakat o yalnız birimizdi. İdrak edebiliyor musunuz?"
